nodes.text: Champagne was an alcoholic beverage. Xizor enjoyed green champagne. Daruvvian champagne was another type. Gavin Darklighter and Sera Faleur had a champagne fountain at their wedding.
A bottle of champagne was once sent to Rebels posing as Henry and Martha Buntwhistle by Egot Pai-4-Yem.
